{
  "stem": "11167.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went to Ostrog.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is the borders-- the old borders from Poland and Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when we came there, we straight away did feel that it is not a good time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the bombing stopped only for the-- for the army, for the German army to walk in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know how they did go out on bikes, on big bikes?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in every bike was arranged to kill you if you going-- you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- that was the first time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then came the heavy army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was on the fourth day when they walk into our town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lately, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was the one at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody was already settled and married, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, because my-- my sister was already in Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She went away in '30.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's-- my brothers straight-- nobody did move.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they was killed-- straight away was killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this one ran away to the same village what-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --but we did sit the 10 days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Money I had.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know why I had money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had a lot of rubles, because you couldn't buy nothing for the rubles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- I don't know if my mother gave me, because she say, take whatever you can take it, because the rubles we will-- we will throw them away, or we will burn them, because it's nothing you buy.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I took about 1,000 or 2,000 rubles, and I divide it between these-- what we went, the whole group, because I was scared to carry money.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had the-- the few jewelries that would help me out to come over the--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then afterwards, a few young people came already from Dubno.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he say, you can't go back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
